title: Multiple people linked to mum girl killings
text:
Multiple people linked to mum, girl killings 
The West Australian Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Police believe they have spoken to people with "actual knowledge" of what happened to Karlie Pearce-Stevenson and her daughter Khandalyce and have linked multiple people with the murders.Investigators says Karlie Pearce-Stevenson was likely killed in or around Belanglo State Forest, with detectives hopeful of making an arrest after turning up more evidence in house searches in South Australia and the ACT yesterday.They are almost certain the young Alice Springs mum was killed in NSW and put her time of death around December 2008, nearly two years before her remains were found.Where and when Kh...
